&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Network design, product selection, routing, configuration and troubleshooting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Closely work with our HPC Systems team, as well as other teams to scale our research environment&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Meet with external parties for project related items as well as future endeavors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Overall capacity planning for the data center networks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop scripts and processes to increase efficiency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with others in the network team to solve cross discipline problems&lt;/li&gt;
