&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Profile&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;10+ years of relevant experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to prioritize workloads and manage implementation schedules with a meticulous attention to detail&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactive problem-solver with the technical skills and hands-on mentality to tackle challenges in the field.&lt;/li&gt;
