&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Skills&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent oral and written communication skills: able to distill complicated issues into clear and concise terms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to create and maintain clear and effective technical documentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In depth understanding of common layer 2 and layer 3 network protocols (OSPF, BGP, PIM, IGMP, RoCEv2, spine-leaf architecture, and VXLAN) and best practices for them&lt;/li&gt;
