&lt;li&gt;Experience managing Arista (EOS), Cisco (NX-OS), Nvidia (Cumulus) and SONiC-based switches, as well as an interest in exploring new platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong design skills in computing and grid networks, with expertise in capacity planning, and full lifecycle project management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with packet decoding and analysis tools such as tcpdump and Wireshark&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ex

